            <div id="sm-cog-elements" class="noprint"></div>
            <div class="allset-page-heading"><h1>Advanced uses of "hai"</h1></div>
            <!-- subtitle -->
            <div id="contentSub" ><span class="mw-redirectedfrom">(Redirected from <a href="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/?title=ASG4807F&amp;redirect=no" class="mw-redirect" title="ASG4807F">ASG4807F</a>)</span></div>
            <!-- /subtitle -->
                        <div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div id="ibox" class="toc">
	<div class="ibox-link"><span class="plainlinks"><a href="ASG4807F" class="mw-redirect" title="ASG4807F"><img src="https&#58;//resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/silk/link.png" /></a></span></div>
	<ul class="ibox-list">
               <li class="ibox-level-cefr-hsk clearfix">
                        
			<div class="ibox-label">Level</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><span style="font-size: 1.4em;"><a href="B2_grammar_points" title="B2 grammar points"> B2</a></span> / <span style="font-size:0.75em;"><a href="HSK5_grammar_points" class="mw-redirect" title="HSK5 grammar points">HSK5</a></span></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-level clearfix" style="display:none">
			<div class="ibox-label">Level</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="B2_grammar_points" title="B2 grammar points"> B2</a></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-level-hsk clearfix" style="display:none;">
			<div class="ibox-label">Level</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="HSK5_grammar_points" class="mw-redirect" title="HSK5 grammar points"> HSK5</a></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-similarto clearfix">
			<div class="ibox-label">Similar to</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><ul class="smw-format ul-format"><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Expressing_&quot;and_also&quot;_with_&quot;hai&quot;" title="Expressing &quot;and also&quot; with &quot;hai&quot;">Expressing "and also" with "hai"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">A2</span></span>)</li><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Continuation_with_&quot;hai&quot;" title="Continuation with &quot;hai&quot;">Continuation with "hai"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">B1</span></span>)</li><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Simple_rhetorical_questions" title="Simple rhetorical questions">Simple rhetorical questions</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">B1</span></span>)</li><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Many_types_of_&quot;not_only..._but_also...&quot;" title="Many types of &quot;not only... but also...&quot;">Many types of "not only... but also..."</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">B2</span></span>)</li></ul></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-similarto-hsk clearfix" style="display:none;">
			<div class="ibox-label">Similar to</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><ul class="smw-format ul-format"><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Continuation_with_&quot;hai&quot;" title="Continuation with &quot;hai&quot;">Continuation with "hai"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">HSK2</span></span>)</li><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Expressing_&quot;and_also&quot;_with_&quot;hai&quot;" title="Expressing &quot;and also&quot; with &quot;hai&quot;">Expressing "and also" with "hai"</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">HSK2</span></span>)</li><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Simple_rhetorical_questions" title="Simple rhetorical questions">Simple rhetorical questions</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">HSK2</span></span>)</li><li class="smw-row"><span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value"><a href="Many_types_of_&quot;not_only..._but_also...&quot;" title="Many types of &quot;not only... but also...&quot;">Many types of "not only... but also..."</a></span></span> (<span class="smw-field"><span class="smw-value">HSK4</span></span>)</li></ul></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-usedfor clearfix">
			<div class="ibox-label">Used for</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="Asking_questions" title="Asking questions">Asking questions</a>, <a href="Expressing_attitude" title="Expressing attitude">Expressing attitude</a>, <a href="Expressing_degree" title="Expressing degree">Expressing degree</a>, <a href="Asking_rhetorical_questions" title="Asking rhetorical questions">Asking rhetorical questions</a> </div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-keywords clearfix">
			<div class="ibox-label">Keywords</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="吗" title="吗">吗</a>, <a href="还" title="还">还</a></div>
		</li>
		
	</ul>
	<div class="ibox-image"><a href="./File:Chinese-grammar-wiki-ma.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Chinese-grammar-wiki-ma.jpg" src="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/b/b6/Chinese-grammar-wiki-ma.jpg/300px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-ma.jpg" decoding="async" width="300" height="300" srcset="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/b/b6/Chinese-grammar-wiki-ma.jpg/450px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-ma.jpg 1.5x, https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/b/b6/Chinese-grammar-wiki-ma.jpg/600px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-ma.jpg 2x" /></a></div>
</div> 
<p>Aside from its <a href="还" title="还">other uses</a>, 还 (hái) can be used to express a surprised or sarcastic tone, and can also be used with rhetorical questions. 
</p>
<div id="toc" class="toc"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2>Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-1"><a href="ASG4807F#Expressing_a_Tone_of_Surprise"><span class="tocnumber">1</span> <span class="toctext">Expressing a Tone of Surprise</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-2"><a href="ASG4807F#Structure"><span class="tocnumber">1.1</span> <span class="toctext">Structure</span></a></li>
