</ul>
</li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-4"><a href="ASG4807F#Expressing_a_Tone_of_Sarcasm"><span class="tocnumber">2</span> <span class="toctext">Expressing a Tone of Sarcasm</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-5"><a href="ASG4807F#Structure_2"><span class="tocnumber">2.1</span> <span class="toctext">Structure</span></a></li>
